openquake.gem-taxonomy (1.12.0)

  [Matteo Nastasi]
  * Revert back namespace declaration after oq-engine packaging improvement.
  * Add python 3.12 to test matrix
  * Add action to automate release publication
  * Add python dictionary format for 'gem-taxonomy-info' format
  * Smart management of requested versions: 3, 3.3, 4 or 4.0 curently
  * Add '-t|--taxonomy-vers <vers>' argument for custom command to specify the taxonomy
    specifications version that you want to use
  * Manage new 'deny' semantic from taxonomy specs in validation, explanation and graph
    rappresentation

